OL,3,CLamb costs soared over last three
OL,4,Cyears due to climate change ` report
OL,6,FHouseholds that eat lamb regularly
OL,7,Fhave seen #168 added to the cost over
OL,8,Fthe last three years due to climate
OL,9,Fchange, according to a report.
OL,11,FWeather "shocks" experienced by the UK
OL,12,Fsince 2022, including droughts,
OL,13,Fextreme heat and heavy rainfall, have
OL,14,Fpushed prices for a typical 2kg leg of
OL,15,Flamb up by between 7% and 21% each
OL,16,Ftime, according to the Energy and
OL,17,FClimate Intelligence Unit (ECIU) think
OL,18,Ftank.
OL,26,@sD@IOUsD@PO]
