OL,3,CLamb costs soared over last three
OL,4,Cyears due to climate change ` report
OL,6,FChris Jaccarini, land, food and
OL,7,Ffarming analyst at the ECIU, said: "As
OL,8,Ffamilies and communities sit down to
OL,9,Fcelebrate this Easter, the cost of
OL,10,Fclimate change is hitting home.
OL,12,F"Lamb prices are through the roof
OL,13,Fafter droughts, extreme heat and heavy
OL,14,Frainfall have hit farmers' costs of
OL,15,Fproduction, weakening grass growth and
OL,16,Fnot allowing the depleted hay stores
OL,17,Fthey depend on time to recover.
OL,26,@oD@dOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
