CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775178189
OL,3,CLamb costs soared over last three
OL,4,Cyears due to climate change ` report
OL,6,F"With beef and dairy prices up after
OL,7,Fsimilar extreme weather impacts on
OL,8,Fproduction, it is clear that climate
OL,9,Fchange now poses a major and worsening
OL,10,Fchallenge for livestock farmers.
OL,12,F"As the current oil price shock
OL,13,Fthreatens to bring yet another round
OL,14,Fof food price inflation, without
OL,15,Ffaster progress towards net zero to
OL,16,Fbring balance back to our climate, as
OL,17,Fwell as more investment in the
OL,18,Fresilience of our farmers, the
OL,19,Faffordability of food is worryingly
OL,20,Fexposed to these worsening shocks."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
