OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775178189
OL,3,CLamb costs soared over last three
OL,4,Cyears due to climate change ` report
OL,6,F"To mitigate this, we now keep fewer
OL,7,Fsheep as that makes it easier to
OL,8,Fmaintain good-quality pasture by
OL,9,Fadopting nature-friendly grazing
OL,10,Fpractices and rotating them around."
OL,12,FAs well as rising lamb prices, the
OL,13,Fcost of Easter eggs has risen by two
OL,14,Fthirds in three years, as heavy
OL,15,Frainfall, droughts, and humid
OL,16,Fheatwaves affected cocoa production in
OL,17,FWest Africa.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@dO]
