OL,3,CLamb costs soared over last three
OL,4,Cyears due to climate change ` report
OL,6,FGrocery inflation figures released
OL,7,Fthis week by Worldpanel by Numerator
OL,8,Fshow the average amount paid for an
OL,9,FEaster egg is 9% higher than last
OL,10,Fyear, up to #3.27.
